** &quot;Sùng Khang&quot; (, 1568–1578): Mạc dynasty—era name of Mạc Mậu Hợp
* Japan
** &quot;Daiei&quot; (, 1521–1528): era name of Emperor Go-Kashiwabara and Emperor Go-Nara
** &quot;Kyōroku&quot; (, 1528–1532): era name of Emperor Go-Nara
** &quot;Tenbun&quot; (, 1532–1555): era name of Emperor Go-Nara
** &quot;Kōji&quot; (, 1555–1558): era name of Emperor Go-Nara and Emperor Ōgimachi
** &quot;Eiroku&quot; (, 1558–1570): era name of Emperor Ōgimachi

